{"tid":2261333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"年輕倉務員涉藏雷射筆被控 警員不肯定被告有否堵路或破壞商店","createTime":"2020-10-28T08:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T09:44:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76ebbc051bdb6aa61e2747eda0ef695c5f8a3d42","tid":2261333,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"去年10月市民發起「十八區開花」，爆發警民衝突。其間一名年輕倉務員在將軍澳街頭被捕，及後在警署被搜出背囊內有雷射筆及噴漆，遭控以管有攻擊性武器等罪。案件今開審，拘捕警員在盤問下同意，他並沒看見被告參與堵路或損壞商店，而單憑被告的衣著，不可肯定他曾參與違法行為。警員又稱，被告被捕時沒戴頭盔、豬嘴、手套或手持任何物品，在現場搜身時也沒發現任何武器，被制服後亦無反抗。<br />\n<br />\n警員20938袁嘉俊今供稱，案發時隸屬機動部隊第二小隊，當晚8時許接到電台通知，指將軍澳有人堵路及破壞商店，另有兩名便衣警遇襲，他遂到將軍澳警署候命。至9時半，他收到指示前往尚德邨一帶進行拘捕行動。當警車駛至唐德街及唐賢街交界時，發現30至40名身穿黑色衫褲及戴帽人士，當中大部份人戴面罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/FVU42GMTD5F6RJ7M3HGBWODLEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FFVU42GMTD5F6RJ7M3HGBWODLEU%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7B%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=e8498ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FFVU42GMTD5F6RJ7M3HGBWODLEU%2F&h=de40f24e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/FVU42GMTD5F6RJ7M3HGBWODLEU/</a>"},{"pid":"2f0ba63d8c77c99ae8a6a98d98d8bc0081ccfe4d","tid":2261333,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"又鳩拉"},{"pid":"72288958e21ff24802b9936b47eec10f47efc166","tid":2261333,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61469769b8d391110a1a7aa78753d6bf55bef67","tid":2261333,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f163af9436984d3f6e35f0959322974645b3842","tid":2261333,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"被制服後亦無反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大步𨈇過無事~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}